scenes.description: Risu decides to head towards the forest on the world map.
Risu encounters an injured dragon in the forest and offers to help.
Risu performs 'The Wolf Fell in Love with Little Red Riding Hood' while riding the dragon.
scenes.song_name: The Wolf Fell in Love with Little Red Riding Hood

scenes.description: Risu heals the dragon with sushi and they prepare to find the monster.
Map transition as they fly towards the sky.

subtitles.original: I should go through the forest next.
subtitles.english: I should go through the forest next.

subtitles.original: Oh no! What happened to you, almighty dragon?
subtitles.english: Oh no! What happened to you, almighty dragon?

subtitles.original: ピンクの巨獣にやられた。今は力が入らん。
subtitles.english: I was beaten by a pink behemoth. I have no strength left.

subtitles.original: 翼も破壊されてしまった。
subtitles.english: My wings have been destroyed as well.

subtitles.original: Oh no, that is bad! I can help you recover if you can take me straight to the giant monster in exchange!
subtitles.english: Oh no, that is bad! I can help you recover if you can take me straight to the giant monster in exchange!

subtitles.original: 任せておけ。
subtitles.english: Leave it to me.

subtitles.original: おおかみは赤ずきんに恋をした
subtitles.english: The Wolf Fell in Love with Little Red Riding Hood

subtitles.original: 偶然から始まる　必然のワンシーン
subtitles.english: One scene of inevitability that begins from a chance encounter

subtitles.original: 遠くに見えたのは　揺れる赤色
subtitles.english: What I saw in the distance was a swaying red color

subtitles.original: 不思議な森の奥で　見つけた黒い影
subtitles.english: In the depths of the mysterious forest, I found a black shadow

subtitles.original: 何かが始まる予感　怖くて逃げ出した
subtitles.english: A premonition that something is starting, I was scared and ran away

subtitles.original: 「出会い」は　終焉へ続く　シナリオ
subtitles.english: An "encounter" is a scenario leading to the end

subtitles.original: だからわざと　遠回りをした
subtitles.english: So I purposely took a detour

subtitles.original: 会いたいなんて　触れたいなんて　話したいなんて　思わない
subtitles.english: I don't think about wanting to meet, wanting to touch, or wanting to talk

subtitles.original: かよわい君と　鋭い僕が　出会う　それが終わりさ
subtitles.english: When frail you and sharp me meet, that's the end

subtitles.original: 残酷だって　罵ったって　運命は変わらない
subtitles.english: Even if you call it cruel or revile it, fate will not change

subtitles.original: ああ　どうして君が？　どうして僕が？　おおかみと赤ずきんなんだ
subtitles.english: Ah, why are you? Why am I? The Wolf and Little Red Riding Hood

subtitles.original: きっと君は今日も　この道を訪れる
subtitles.english: Surely you will visit this road again today

subtitles.original: そして僕は今日も　ずっと見守るしかできない
subtitles.english: And I can do nothing but watch over you today as well

subtitles.original: 君はあの木の先で　いつも通り隠れてる
subtitles.english: You are hiding beyond that tree, just like always

subtitles.original: 私は気づかぬふりしたまま　通り過ぎた
subtitles.english: I passed by while pretending not to notice

subtitles.original: 視線は　交わらない　声は　届かない
subtitles.english: Our gazes don't meet, our voices don't reach

subtitles.original: ため息だけが　虚しく重なる
subtitles.english: Only sighs overlap in vain

subtitles.original: 会えなくたって　触れなくたって　話せなくたって　いいから
subtitles.english: It's okay even if we can't meet, can't touch, or can't talk

subtitles.original: 頼りない君と　ぎこちない僕が　そこにいるだけでいいんだ
subtitles.english: It's enough just for frail you and awkward me to be there

subtitles.original: これが恋だって　言わないなら　言葉なんてなくていい
subtitles.english: If you won't call this love, then words aren't needed

subtitles.original: 考えたって　考えたって　エンディングは変わらない
subtitles.english: No matter how much I think, the ending won't change

subtitles.original: 会いたかったんだ　触れたかったんだ　話したかった　本当は
subtitles.english: I wanted to meet you, I wanted to touch you, I wanted to talk to you, truth be told

subtitles.original: かわいい君と　優しい僕が　出会い　結ばれるエンド
subtitles.english: An end where cute you and kind me meet and are tied together

subtitles.original: 何回だって　何回だって　神様に願ったよ
subtitles.english: Time and time again, I prayed to God

subtitles.original: でも　悲しいくらい　悲しいくらい　おおかみと赤ずきんなんだ
subtitles.english: But, sadly, so sadly, we are the Wolf and Little Red Riding Hood

subtitles.original: 泣いている君を　慰めたくて　伸ばした腕が震える
subtitles.english: Wanting to comfort you who are crying, my outstretched arm trembles

subtitles.original: 愛しているよ　抱きしめたいよ　だけど　できないんだよ
subtitles.english: I love you, I want to hold you, but I can't

subtitles.original: どうあがいたって　どう願ったって　爪も牙も消えない
subtitles.english: No matter how I struggle, no matter how I pray, my claws and fangs won't disappear

subtitles.original: だから　ただ待ってるよ　君の涙が止むまで　あの木の先で
subtitles.english: So I'll just wait, until your tears stop, beyond that tree

subtitles.original: Ah, here it is! If you eat this, you can recover super quick!
subtitles.english: Ah, here it is! If you eat this, you can recover super quick!

subtitles.original: 感謝する。
subtitles.english: I'm grateful.

subtitles.original: よし、完全復活だ。
subtitles.english: Alright, I'm fully recovered.

subtitles.original: 今すぐ怪獣の元へ案内しよう。
subtitles.english: I'll guide you to the monster right now.

subtitles.original: Okay, let's go!
subtitles.english: Okay, let's go!

subtitles.original: FLY HIGH!!
subtitles.english: FLY HIGH!!

subtitles.original: 飛べ　FLY HIGH!!　汗と血と涙で
subtitles.english: Fly, FLY HIGH!! With sweat, blood, and tears
